### Enhancements

* Add `conda.cli.actions.LazyMixin` to support lazy evaluated fields for ArgumentParser arguments. (#15244)
* Add `conda.plugins.types.CondaExperiementalFeature` plugin type allowing downstream packages to extend the experimental feature selection that can be toggled via `--experimental`. (#15239 via #15244)

### Bug fixes

* <news item>

### Deprecations

* Mark `conda.cli.helpers.LazyChoicesAction` as pending deprecation, to remove in 26.9. Use `conda.cli.actions.LazyStoreAction` instead. (#15244)

